ckson (American football coach)|Fred Jackson]], American football player and coach * 1950 &ndash; [[Giorgos Kastrinakis]], Greek-American basketball player *[[1951]] &ndash; [[Michael Patrick Cronan]], American graphic designer and academic (d. 2013) * 1951 &ndash; [[James Newton Howard]], American composer, conductor, and producer * 1951 &ndash; [[Dave Parker]], American baseball player and coach * 1951 &ndash; [[Brian Taylor (basketball)|Brian Taylor]], American basketball player *[[1952]] &ndash; [[Uzi Hitman]], Israeli singer-songwriter (d. 2004) * 1952 &ndash; [[Billy Knight]], American basketball player *[[1953]] &ndash; [[Ken Navarro]], Italian-American guitarist and composer *[[1954]] &ndash; [[Pete Byrne]], English singer-songwriter ([[Naked Eyes]]) * 1954 &ndash; [[Paul Chapman (musician)|Paul Chapman]], Welsh guitarist and songwriter * 1954 &ndash; [[Gregory Maguire]], American author * 1954 &ndash; [[Elizabeth May]], American-Canadian environmentalist, lawyer, and politician * 1954 &ndash; [[George Pérez]], American author and illustrator *[[1956]] &ndash; [[Berit Aunli]], Norwegian skiier *1956 &ndash; [[Patricia Cornwell]], American journalist and author *1956 &ndash; [[Marek Gazdzicki]], Polish nuclear physicist *1956 &ndash; [[Joaquín (footballer, born 1956)|Joaquín]], Spanish footballer *1956 &ndash; [[John Le Lievre]], British squash player *1956 &ndash; [[Kayhan Mortezavi]], Iranian director *1956 &ndash; [[Francine Raymond]], French Canadian singer songwriter *1956 &ndash; [[Nikolai Tsonev]], Bulgarian politician *1956 &ndash; [[Rudolf Wojtowicz]], Polish footballer *[[1957]] &ndash; [[Randy Read]], English crystallographer and academic *[[1958]] &ndash; [[David Ancrum]], American basketball player and coach *[[1959]] &ndash; [[Peter Fowler]], Australian golfer *[[1960]] &ndash; [[Steve Paikin]], Canadian journalist and author *[[1961]] &ndash; [[Thomas Benson (American football)|Thomas Benson]], American football player * 1961 &ndash; [[Michael 